---
title: HelloHero: Ginger Pork & Veggie Stir-Fry with Nutty Garlic Rice
description: A zap of ginger, a splash of oyster sauce and for the final ingredient in our flavour potion, a good dollop of sweet chilli sauce. Dip the pork into it and watch as a delicious dinner comes to life before your eyes. This pork and veggie stir-fry will be irresistible to anyone who takes a bite. Simply magical!
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.
